Subject: [PATCH 08/12] Fix Excalidraw rendering - read files from disk and add
 freedraw support

- Replace pako with lz-string for proper LZ-String decompression
- Read original markdown files from disk to access content before OFM removes %% comments
- Add support for freedraw, line, and arrow element types in client-side renderer
- Successfully decompress and render user's ex-test.md drawing
